5, 123.4]}, {"text": "Item 5.", "bbox": [127.5, 127.8, 235.8, 164.7]}, {"text": "Market for the Registrant’s Common Equity, Related", "bbox": [307.4, 127.8, 1079.6, 164.7]}, {"text": "Stockholder Matters and Issuer Purchases of Equity", "bbox": [307.5, 166.1, 1060.3, 203.1]}, {"text": "Securities", "bbox": [307.5, 204.4, 454.7, 241.3]}, {"text": "Cincinnati Financial Corporation had approximately 12,000 shareholders of record as of December 31, 2006.", "bbox": [127.5, 245.6, 1094.1, 269.3]}, {"text": "Many of our independent agent representatives and most of the 4,048 associates of our subsidiaries own the", "bbox": [127.5, 269.3, 1095.4, 292.9]}, {"text": "company’s common stock. We are unable to accurately quantify those holdings because many are beneficially", "bbox": [127.5, 292.9, 1098.0, 316.5]}, {"text": "held.", "bbox": [127.5, 316.5, 176.2, 340.2]}, {"text": "Our common shares are traded under the symbol CINF on the Nasdaq Global Select Market. The common", "bbox": [127.5, 346.4, 1058.9, 370.0]}, {"text": "stock prices and dividend data below reflects the 5 percent stock dividend paid April 26, 2005.", "bbox": [127.5, 370.0, 971.4, 393.7]}, {"text": "Our ability to pay cash dividends may depend on the ability of our insurance subsidiary to pay dividends to the", "bbox": [127.5, 565.0, 1094.5, 588.7]}, {"text": "parent company. The dividend restrictions of our insurance company subsidiaries are discussed in Item 8,", "bbox": [127.5, 588.6, 1061.4, 612.3]}, {"text": "Note 8 to the Consolidated Financial Statements, Page 93.", "bbox": [127.5, 612.3, 654.2, 635.9]}, {"text": "Information regarding securities authorized for issuance under our equity compensation plans appears in the", "bbox": [127.5, 642.1, 1088.5, 665.8]}, {"text": "Proxy Statement under “Securities Authorized for Issuance under Equity Compensation Plans.” This portion of", "bbox": [127.5, 665.7, 1092.1, 689.4]}, {"text": "the Proxy Statement is incorporated herein by reference. Additional information about share-based", "bbox": [127.5, 689.4, 997.7, 713.0]}, {"text": "compensation granted under our equity compensation plans is available in Item 8, Note 16 to the Consolidated", "bbox": [127.5, 713.0, 1108.2, 736.6]}, {"text": "Financial Statements, Page 100.", "bbox": [127.5, 736.6, 420.2, 760.3]}, {"text": "The board of directors has authorized share repurchases since 1996. We discuss the board authorization in", "bbox": [127.5, 766.5, 1078.2, 790.1]}, {"text": "Item 7, Uses of Capital, Page 63. In 2006, we repurchased a total of 2,646,787 shares.", "bbox": [127.5, 790.1, 901.6, 813.8]}, {"text": "(1) Includes 34,343 acquired in 2006, primarily in satisfaction of withholding taxes due upon exercise of stock options.", "bbox": [127.5, 1251.9, 1086.7, 1273.2]}, {"text": "(2) The current repurchase program was announced on August 19, 2005, and became effective on September 1, 2005.", "bbox": [127.5, 1273.2, 1089.1, 1294.4]}, {"text": "It replaced a program which had been in effect since 1999. No repurchase program has expired during the period", "bbox": [165.0, 1294.4, 1066.3, 1315.7]}, {"text": "covered by the above table.", "bbox": [165.0, 1315.7, 387.4, 1336.9]}, {"text": "All of the repurchases reported in the table above were repurchased under our 2005 program, which was", "bbox": [127.5, 1339.9, 1056.0, 1363.5]}, {"text": "approved for 10 million shares. At the time the 1999 program, which was for 17 million shares, was", "bbox": [127.5, 1363.5, 1007.3, 1387.2]}, {"text": "superseded by the 2005 program, it had 2,739,942 shares remaining. Neither of the programs had an", "bbox": [127.5, 1387.1, 1034.0, 1410.8]}, {"text": "expiration date but no further repurchases will occur under the 1999 program.", "bbox": [127.5, 1410.6, 826.4, 1434.3]}]}